To Connection 2,3-4 Linux Servers:

Follow 3 Steps:

1.Update Root Password:
passwd root
Set password
 
2.Modify Configurations:
vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config
Line number :65 , 40 modify to Yes, and remove comments (#)

3.Restart SSHD:
systemctl restart sshd

Generate Public/Private key in Master server or Main Server:
ssh-keygen

Copy Public key to remaning Servers:
ssh-copy-id root@private_IP_address

